graph = hg.HyperGraph()
a, b = graph.new_variables([5, 6])
result = np.sqrt(a)
assert_almost_equal(result.value, np.sqrt(5))
graph.compute(result)
g = graph.g()
h = graph.h()
assert_array_almost_equal(g, [1 / (2 * np.sqrt(5)), 0])
assert_array_almost_equal(h, [[-1 / (20 * np.sqrt(5)), 0], [0, 0]])
